==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clamatores
<hw>Clam`a*to"res</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>clamator</ets>, pl. <ets>clamatores</ets>, a bawler.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A division of passerine birds in which the vocal
muscles are but little developed, so that they lack the power of
singing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clamatorial</ent>⟦br⟧
